Play music via ratpoison

quick hack to play a regex-generated playlist from ratpoison, pause/resume, stop and next needs mplayer

bindings:
bind P exec ( .ratpoison/play.sh ; exit 0 ) #play
bind n exec ( killall mplayer ; exit 0 ) #next
bind h exec killall -STOP mplayer #halt
bind g exec killall -CONT mplayer #go
bind d exec killall play.sh #destroy :)



by ecraven
